   <br>
Cripple or like spells will gain you just as much agro as slow so I only use it on big mobs and then I wait another 10% or more after slowing the mob and as earlier if I still get agro I will stand there and trust my raid to do what they are there for. Any other course for me is foolish. I have tried the run around strategy and not only do I die but it could lead to a wipe out in a domino effect.<br>
